    • Constructor Detail

      • LsaChangeArgument

        public LsaChangeArgument(IEnvironment<List<? extends ILsaMolecule>> environment,
                         ILsaNode node,
                         String[] listTarget,
                         String targetVariab,
                         RandomEngine random)
        Builds a new action that test neighbors which contain in their lsaSpace an lsaMolecule matching . The effect of this Action is to add to the matches map the variable PreferredType (the most present type in neighborhood). The execution has no effect on influenced molecule of reaction.
        Parameters:
        environment - The environment to use
        node - The source node
        listTarget - Gradients list
        targetVariab - Variable name
        random - Random engine
